  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And before-- when this was announced, this general-- give me his name-- anyway-- looked over at me-- I was sitting at the end of the interpreter's bench-- and with a little piece of paper, sort of waving a piece of paper, which I took to mean he wanted to write a-- wanted me to take a note.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I accepted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said yes, send the note over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in this note, he wrote down, he said, I have noticed that when your interpreters have a pre-prepared translation to read from, the effect is much better than if they just do it off the-- off the microphone.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If I prepare my final statement in advance, will you translate it for me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I wrote him back, of course, you give me the translation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he sent me this translation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was looking for that a minute ago, and I-- I didn't find it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What it was was a 3/4 page statement in which he said, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when I entered my military career, I was taught that the highest loyalty to which one owed-- the highest loyalty which one owed was one's own country.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, he says, I'm sitting here listening to this, and I hear people saying the highest entity to which one owes loyalty is humanity at large.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, he says, if the world is to proceed in this way and to be improved in this way, and he says, I belong then to the older generation which is left behind, and the new generation takes over.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He says, I will-- if that is to be the case, he says, I will gladly accept my punishment, whatever it may be, because I believe this is a progress to a higher level of moral standards.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
